{"tid":433961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日生飛滋又勁難好返","createTime":"2017-10-13T00:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T00:51:00.000Z","uid":20228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2bbe629fe41f736e9a34d8f66d8a9aa2ef1da491","tid":433961,"uid":20228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:12:00.000Z","msg":"之前睇過醫生，醫生話係因為壓力所以會生飛滋。<br />\n<br />\n我sem break 既時候一粒飛滋都唔會生，但開sem之後就一波接一波咁生，又或者一次過生兩粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常每粒都要兩個禮拜多啲先至好得翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係類似咁樣？可以食啲咩生少啲同埋好返得快啲？真係好痛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb5ef10ad13490d4d545d488051e65f70933518","tid":433961,"uid":35630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"飲多d牛奶 or直接食b雜"},{"pid":"6771da73e255b88e1c60ecc6ca0f31a67a24459a","tid":433961,"uid":84801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲多d牛奶 or直接食b雜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛奶咁燥，會唔會生多幾粒"},{"pid":"9267e3fe6e9b1b3ddd47377457b7775348010747","tid":433961,"uid":20228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲多d牛奶 or直接食b雜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nB雜同葉酸我都有時不時食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f8f0b4f0479e8801af804c438e40d706e5ff54","tid":433961,"uid":20228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲多d牛奶 or直接食b雜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛奶咁燥，會唔會生多幾粒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死啦，會唔會關牛奶事？我都會每朝早飲牛奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33219554d7cb83b16b360a02842749da2680e3d","tid":433961,"uid":71343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockqu